en.description:
I took sawdust, some glue and made a real beauty for the home. This is a very simple decor for different objects that everyone can repeat. Sawdust is a great and cheap craft material.

Here's what you need:
• Various items for decoration;
• Sandpaper, nail polish remover;
• Sawdust;
• PVA glue;
• Paint in spray cans;
• Varnish in a spray can.

Watch this video to find out what you can do with sawdust and glue.

And also, take a look at our interesting works:

6 cool plastic bottle craft ideas for garden, cottage and vegetable garden: https://youtu.be/o0Rnnutfxew

How to make a cardboard box with your own hands: https://youtu.be/NADKrfrxM9w

12 ideas on how to make a texture from putty with improvised means: https://youtu.be/LsAhv9ATaOY

5 plastic container flower pot ideas: https://youtu.be/FwA0tWvc1Bo

